    - "multiprocessing.TimeoutError.__mro__[1].__name__ == 'ProcessError' (len=12); TimeoutError's direct base is ProcessError."
    - "All expected values verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
