invariant multiprocessing_extra154.te_mro_len_5:
  description: "multiprocessing.TimeoutError.__mro__.__len__() == 5 — MRO is (TimeoutError, ProcessError, Exception, BaseException, object); TimeoutError and AuthenticationError are sibling subclasses of ProcessError with identical MRO depth; TimeoutError.__mro__.__len__(5) == AuthenticationError.__mro__.__len__(5); TimeoutError.__mro__.__len__(5) > ProcessError.__mro__.__len__(4) by 1; verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11"
